{{Lunisolar October}} 
'''October 26''' is the 26th day of month {{ill|October (Lunisolar)|ja|10月 (旧暦)|lt=Kannazuki|1=Kannazuki|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}  the 10th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} . It's {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}  day is {{ill|Taian|ja|大安|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} . 

== Events ==
* {{ill|Kyushu|ja|久寿|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 2nd year（{{ill|Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1155|ja|1155|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|November 22|ja|11月22日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） - 雅仁親王が即位して第77代・{{ill|Emperor Go-Shirakawa|ja|Emperor Go-Shirakawa|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} に{{要出典|date=2021-02}} 
* {{ill|Kan'ō|ja|Kan'ō|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 1st year/{{ill|Shōhei|ja|正平 (日本)|lt=Shōhei|lt_ja=正平|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 5th year（{{ill|Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1350|ja|1350|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|November 26|ja|11月26日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） - {{ill|Kan'ō Disturbance|ja|Kan'ōの擾乱|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 。将軍・{{ill|Ashikaga Takauji|ja|Ashikaga Takauji|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} と対立していた弟・{{ill|Ashikaga Naoyoshi|ja|足利直義|lt=Naoyoshi|lt_ja=直義|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} が、京都を脱出して挙兵
* {{ill|Tenpō|ja|天保|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 9th year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1838|ja|1838|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|December 12|ja|12月12日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） - {{ill|Tenrikyo|ja|天理教|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 開教

== Births ==
* {{ill|Anwa|ja|安和|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 1st year（{{ill|968|ja|968|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|November 19|ja|11月19日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） - {{ill|Emperor Hanayama|ja|花山天皇|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 、65代{{ill|Emperor|ja|天皇|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} （+ {{ill|1008|ja|1008|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ）
* {{ill|Genroku|ja|Genroku|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 9th year（{{ill|1696|ja|1696|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|November 20|ja|11月20日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） - {{ill|Tokugawa Suneharu|ja|徳川宗春|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 、7代{{ill|Owari Domain|ja|尾張藩|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 主（+ {{ill|1764|ja|1764|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ）

== Deaths ==
* {{ill|Ōchō|ja|応長|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 1st year（{{ill|1311|ja|1311|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|December 6|ja|12月6日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） - {{ill|Hojo Sadatoki|ja|北条貞時|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 、{{ill|Kamakura Shogunate|ja|鎌倉幕府|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 9代{{ill|Shikken|ja|Shikken|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ・8代{{ill|Tokusō|ja|得宗|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} （* {{ill|1271|ja|1271|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ）

