'''October 26''' is the 26th day of month {{ill|October (Lunisolar)|ja|10月 (旧暦)|lt=October (Kannazuki)|1=Kannazuki|2=ja|3=10月 (旧暦)|1=Kannazuki|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/October (Lunisolar)|13=User:Immanuelle/Kannazuki|qq=}}  the 10th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=}} . It's {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Rokuyō|qq=}}  day is {{ill|Taian|ja|大安|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Taian|qq=}} . 

== Events ==
* {{ill|Kyushu|ja|久寿|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kyushu|qq=}} 2nd year（{{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|1155|ja|1155|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1155|qq=}} {{ill|November 22|ja|11月22日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/November 22|qq=}} ） - 雅仁親王が即位して第77代・{{ill|Emperor Go-Shirakawa|ja|Emperor Go-Shirakawa|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Emperor Go-Shirakawa|qq=}} に{{Citation needed|date=2021-02|qq=}} 
* {{ill|Kan'ō|ja|Kan'ō|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kan'ō|qq=}} 1st year/{{ill|Shōhei|ja|正平 (日本)|lt=Shōhei|lt_ja=正平|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Shōhei|qq=}} 5th year（{{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|1350|ja|1350|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1350|qq=}} {{ill|November 26|ja|11月26日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/November 26|qq=}} ） - {{ill|Kan'ō Disturbance|ja|Kan'ōの擾乱|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kan'ō Disturbance|qq=}} 。将軍・{{ill|Ashikaga Takauji|ja|Ashikaga Takauji|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ashikaga Takauji|qq=}} と対立していた弟・{{ill|Ashikaga Naoyoshi|ja|足利直義|lt=Naoyoshi|lt_ja=直義|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ashikaga Naoyoshi|qq=}} が、京都を脱出して挙兵
* {{ill|Tenpō|ja|天保|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tenpō|qq=}} 9th year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|1838|ja|1838|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1838|qq=}} {{ill|December 12|ja|12月12日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/December 12|qq=}} ） - {{ill|Tenrikyo|ja|天理教|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tenrikyo|qq=}} 開教

